data.description: This FIVE bedroom beauty in Walden on Lake Houston is ready for new owners! Five bedrooms and 3.5 baths PLUS a game room/bonus room. Bring your people and/or your pets or keep this one all to yourself. There is plenty of room to spread out! The kitchen overlooks the family room with fireplace with gas logs. Spacious kitchen with granite countertops, lots of storage and prep space. Generously sized primary bedroom downstairs. Primary bath has double sinks, separate tub and shower. All other bedrooms are upstairs. Looking for a blank slate? Fresh paint throughout will accomodate any decor style. Enjoy Sunday Funday on the back patio with your custom built wood fired pizza oven! You don't want to miss this one. ~ Call your agent today to schedule a showing. Then start boxing up your stuff and get ready to MOVE!!
